subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Unfamiliarity reigned in the women’s singles semifinals at Wimbledon as Vera Zvonareva, the 21st seed, advanced and will play Serena Williams in the women’s final Saturday.
